# n1k1 sidecar (DESIGN-indexing.md): built secondary-index / derived artifacts
# (data.bolt, bleve/, zone-maps, manifests) are regenerable -- ignore them at any
# depth. catalog.json is the declared source of truth, so keep it trackable.
**/.n1k1/*
!**/.n1k1/catalog.json

# n1k1 WebAssembly demo build outputs (regenerate with web/wasm/build.sh)
/web/n1k1.wasm
/web/wasm_exec.js
# local patched dependency copies for the wasm build (host-specific)
/.wasm-mods/
